          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Reality:</strong> If you cancel after 6 months, most don't prorate refunds. You overpaid.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">‚ö†Ô∏è Tier Traps: Basic Plan is Useless</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Basic tier: No custom domain, builder branding, no ecommerce. Who wants that?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Reality:</strong> Pro tier is the real minimum. That $9/mo price? It's $15-25/mo for actual use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">‚ö†Ô∏è Price Hikes After Year 1</h3>
