        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-[3px] border-blue-400 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2">üí∞ Best Budget Option: Hostinger ($2.99-16/mo)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Unbeatable price for basic sites. But you'll outgrow it quickly. Good for testing, not long-term.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
            <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Cheapest hosting</span>
            <span class="bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Good for testing</span>
