        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-[3px] border-purple-400 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">üõí Best for E-commerce: 10Web ($10-60/mo)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Only AI builder that scales to real online stores. WooCommerce integration means serious ecommerce.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
