      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Free Tier Reality Check</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-gray-400">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Free tiers are for testing, not production.</strong></p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">Every builder limits free plans: no custom domain, builder branding, feature caps. They're generous trials, not free lunch.</p>
